		  将PCF8591的IN0接可调电阻的AD1
		  将PCF8591的OUT外接万用表的表笔(用电压档)
          	   STK169P+     			STK162+
			   PORTC	---------   LED0~7
				
		 	  DVK500				 STK162+
				VCC		---------	  VCC
				GND		---------	  GND
				SDA	 	---------	  PA0
				SCK		---------	  PA1
